headline: FIS Wins ALM Solution of the Year at Risk Asia Awards 2025
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., October 29, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced that FIS Balance Sheet Manager has been awarded "ALM Solution of the Year" at the prestigious Risk Asia Awards 2025. This recognition underscores FIS’ commitment to providing modern, cloud-based technology that empowers financial institutions to manage risks effectively and unlock growth while money is in motion.
